data.title: Secretary Cohen is welcomed by President Zine El Abidine Ben Ali at the Presidential Palace in Tunis, Tunisia.
data.text: Secretary of Defense William S. Cohen (left) is welcomed by President Zine El Abidine Ben Ali at the Presidential Palace in Tunis, Tunisia, on Oct. 7, 2000. The two men will meet to discuss a broad range of international security issues of interest to both nations. Cohen's stop in Tunisia came at the start of a three nation visit which will also take him to Greece and the United Kingdom.
